86.title: Psycho Kid Kills Father
86.plot: Jesse escapes from the room and attempts to get his money back.

1.title: Psycho Dad Destroys Xbox
1.plot: After mischievous 20 year old Jesse Ridgeway is caught playing video games on his Father's TV, his precious gaming console becomes a vital target for him, during the chaos of this event, Jesse's brother manages to catch it all on camera.

2.title: Psycho Brothers Filming Freakout
2.plot: To get revenge on his brother for filming their dad destroying Jesse's X-Box, the latter decides to destroy something his brother cherishes the most, his camera.

3.title: Psycho Dad Axes Laptop
3.plot: To get revenge on Jeffery for destroying his camera, Jesse attempts to bring the person who knows punishment best to him. Psycho Dad.

4.title: Psycho Brother Clips Hair
4.plot: Jeffrey cuts some of Jesse's beloved hair off while he's asleep, then Psycho Dad intervenes.

5.title: Psycho Dad Shreds Video Games
5.plot: Concerned about his son's future, an angry father runs over his son's video game collection with a lawn mower.

6.title: Psycho Kid Smashes TV
6.plot: Jesse breaks his Father's television with a baseball bat.

7.title: Psycho Dad Drowns Xbox
7.plot: An enraged father catches Jesse playing Halo Reach on his XBOX so he throws it into the pool.

8.title: Psycho Dad Wrecks Car
8.plot: A crazy father smashes his son's car to pieces.

9.title: The Juggies Powwow -- My Gaming History and Future
9.plot: Jesse talks about how he started gaming on Nintendo, Xbox and Playstation when he was just a wee lad.

10.title: Psycho Kid's Halloween Bloodbath
10.plot: On the night before Halloween, Jeffrey and his Dad pretend to chainsaw Jesse to death...with lots and lots of ketchup.

12.title: Psycho Dad Chainsaws Xbox One
12.plot: An enraged father destroys his son's Xbox One with a chainsaw. (This takes place the night of the Halo: MCC midnight launch.)

13.title: Broken Xbox One *UPDATE*
13.plot: Jesse talks about his destroyed Xbox One.

14.title: Mommy Threw Me an X-Bone
14.plot: Jesse gets a brand new Xbox One, "The Knight".

15.title: Psycho Kid Ruins Thanksgiving
15.plot: An angry gamer freaks out on his Dad during Thanksgiving dinner.

16.title: The Juggies Powwow -- Depression
16.plot: Jesse discusses depression and some possible ways to help combat it.

17.title: Psycho Family Apology
17.plot: Jesse apologizes to his family for ruining Thanksgiving. Matters get worse when Jesse's Dad questions his ability to make a living off of Youtube and video games.

18.title: Fan Mail Monday #1 - People Like Me?
18.plot: The first installment of a new weekly video, "Fan Mail Monday with McJuggerNuggets," where Jesse opens mail sent to him by Juggies.

19.title: Psycho Kid Torches Christmas Tree
19.plot: An angry gamer sets fire to the family Christmas tree because he doesn't get a Wii U.

20.title: Wii U for Christmas *UPDATE*
20.plot: My Mom got me a Nintendo Wii U for Christmas even after setting fire to the family Christmas Tree.

21.title: I GOT MY TWITCH PARTNERSHIP!
21.plot: Jesse announces his Twitch Partnership and encourages everyone to come out and support the live stream.

22.title: Psycho Dad Raids Stream
22.plot: An angry Father barges in on his son's gaming stream and destroys his monitor.

23.title: Broken Monitor & Stream Raid *UPDATE*
23.plot: Jesse updates everyone on the current situation between him and his family. He also talks about the future of the stream and to not send him fan mail money.

24.title: Psycho Girlfriend Breaks iPad
24.plot: Jeffrey's girlfriend, Kate, goes insane and shatters his precious iPad.

25.title: Broken iPad *UPDATE*
25.plot: Jesse talks about the aftermath of "Psycho Girlfriend Breaks iPad". The shattered iPad is shown, on top of Jeffrey's current relationship status.

26.title: Psycho Dad Shatters Youtube Play Button
26.plot: For 500,000 Subscribers, Jesse attempts to do a celebratory house tour and family reaction video. Things turn ugly when Jeffrey steals the Youtube Play Button and their Dad tries to intervene.

27.title: Shattered Youtube Play Button *UPDATE*
27.plot: Jesse talks about the aftermath of his Play Button getting destroyed by his Father in the 500K celebration video.

28.title: Psycho Dad Pounds Nintendo DS
28.plot: While on a trip to London, an angry Father smashes his son's Nintendo DS for playing it non-stop.

29.title: Broken Nintendo DS & My London Experience *UPDATE*
29.plot: Jesse talks about his broken DS after his Father smashed it in London. He also discusses his experience while in England.

30.title: Psycho Brother's Frozen Lockout
30.plot: Jeffrey locks his angry little brother, Jesse, outside of the house in the snow. Jesse is reduced to nothing but his Walking Dead underpants and is forced to parade around in the freezing cold.

31.title: McJuggerNuggets Meetup & Frozen Lockout *UPDATE*
31.plot: Jesse announces the first ever "McJuggerNuggets Meetup" and talks about what happened to the Frozen Lockout video.

32.title: Psycho Dad Crashes WoW LAN Party
32.plot: An angry Father invades his son's "World of Warcraft" LAN party and wreaks havoc.

33.title: LAN Party & Broken Laptops *UPDATE*
33.plot: Jesse talks about the aftermath of the "World of Warcraft" LAN party that got raided by his brother and Father.

34.title: Are the Psycho Videos Real? (q&a #1)
34.plot: Jesse reveals all in this first edition of a "Question and Answer" Series. The true nature of the "Psycho Series" is revealed on top of some general things about Jesse and his family.

35.title: TROPHY DESTRUCTION *Psycho Revenge*
35.plot: Jesse and Jeffrey share their diabolical plan to get back at their "Psycho Dad".

36.title: Psycho Dad Grills Wii U
36.plot: An angry Father torches his son's Nintendo Wii U on the grill after having his childhood trophies destroyed.

37.title: KICKED OUT of the HOUSE *PSYCHO UPDATE*
37.plot: Jesse ventures back into his house to get supplies after being kicked out by his father.

38.title: THE STORM HAS ARRIVED! *UPDATE*
38.plot: Jesse sets up his tent, "The Eagle's Nest", in his territory referred to as: "Eagle's Landing". A fierce storm hits forcing Jesse to receive additional supplies and shelter.

39.title: Welcome to Eagle's Landing
39.plot: Jesse comes to terms with his exile and embraces his new place of residence, "Eagle's Landing". Juliette, his girlfriend, even comes to pay a visit.

40.title: DISCOVERING ELECTRICITY!
40.plot: Jesse and Juliette venture off to find lighting for the tent, only to find something much, much better.

41.title: EXPANDING the ALLIANCE!
41.plot: Jesse says goodbye to Juliette and gets treated to a free lunch by the Eagle's Landing Alliance.

42.title: Donnie Darko Easter Bunny Prank
42.plot: A couple nights before Easter, Frank the Bunny (From "Donnie Darko") scares a young couple while they are camping in the woods.

43.title: BETRAYED by a JUGGIE!
43.plot: On Easter's Eve, Jesse supplies electricity to the Eagle's Nest. Also, a Juggie attempts to alert Psycho Dad of Eagle's Landing's whereabouts.

44.title: JESSE CRASHES EASTER!
44.plot: After learning that he wouldn't be invited to Easter, Jesse decides to go anyway.

45.title: Fan Mail Monday #18 - Eagle's Post/exile Edition
45.plot: While kicked out of his house, Jesse receives close to 50 pieces of mail from the "Eagle's Post". He opens them all while outside of his tent.

46.title: A BETTER DIABOLICAL PLAN!!!
46.plot: Jesse retracts his diabolical plan and decides to do things the right way.

47.title: THE SUPPLY RUN!
47.plot: Jesse makes a supply run to Walmart so he can survive in Eagle's Landing.

48.title: PLANNING the RAID!
48.plot: While experiencing an intense rain storm, Jesse discusses his new plan to sneak back into the house.

49.title: THE BREAK-IN!
49.plot: Jesse raids his house to retrieve some video games for the tent. Unexpected things occur.

50.title: BUILDING the GAMING LAIR!
50.plot: Jesse does some Spring cleaning around the tent and also pimps it out with some gaming stuff.

51.title: THE WARNING SHOT!
51.plot: Jesse's Dad calls a meeting on the driveway to set forth some ground rules.

52.title: MY CURRENT SITUATION
52.plot: Jesse feels defeated after the encounter with his Dad the night before and talks about he thinks this may be it.

53.title: EAGLE's LANDING HAS VISITORS!
53.plot: Jesse struggles to find warmth and also meets up with a couple friends.

54.title: A DAY in the LIFE! (Tent Edition)
54.plot: Jesse walks everyone through a day in his life while he's kicked out of the house. He talks about his morning ritual, showers, poop stories and his diet.

55.title: HUNTING & EXPLORING!
55.plot: Jesse looks for things to pimp out "Eagle's Landing" and goes on a ridiculous trek through the woods with his trusty hatchet.

56.title: LIGHTING the SIGNAL FIRE!
56.plot: Jesse goes bat-shit crazy and decides to light a fire with the intentions of pissing off his Father.

57.title: MESSAGE from PSYCHO DAD
57.plot: Jesse learns that his electricity doesn't work and goes to investigate.

58.title: GENERATING POWER!
58.plot: After learning he's not allowed to use the electric from the garage, Jesse attempts to get the generator started.

59.title: FLIGHT of the EAGLES!
59.plot: Jesse reveals a plan to stand his ground while also re-locating to "Phoenix Landing".

60.title: Psycho Dad Flattens Gaming Lair
60.plot: An angry Father plows over his son's "gaming tent" for using his electricity.

61.title: THE FALL of EAGLE's LANDING *PSYCHO UPDATE*
61.plot: Jesse mourns the loss of his gaming tent and decides to storm the house for his belongings. He then seeks refuge at a friend's house.

62.title: BACK to CIVILIZATION!
62.plot: Jesse gets a legitimate shower and shaves off his grotesque beard.

63.title: A TRIBUTE to EAGLE's LANDING!
63.plot: A sad montage that chronicles the events that transpired after Jesse's gets kicked out of the house. It shows the rise and fall of "Eagle's Landing".

64.title: MY BROTHER's YOUTUBE CHANNEL!
64.plot: Jesse talks about his plans to leave Zack's house while also addressing Jeffrey's new Youtube channel.

65.title: THE JOURNEY to PENNSYLVANIA!
65.plot: Jesse leaves Zack's house to go stay with his girlfriend, Juliette, for an unknown amount of days.

66.title: JESSE and JULIETTE's DAY OFF!
66.plot: Jesse and Juliette take a trip to go get sushi and play around in the park.

67.title: MY UNCLE's INVITATION
67.plot: Jesse and Juliette go on another supply run. Jesse also gets an interesting phone call from his Uncle.

68.title: BETHLEHEM BOREDOM BONANZA!
68.plot: Jesse and Juliette take a leisurely trip to Bethlehem, Pennsylvania.

69.title: A TRIP to ICE CREAM WORLD!
69.plot: Jesse and Juliette go get ice cream and then film a cover of "See You Again" from Fast and Furious 7.

70.title: THE HOMELESS YOUTUBER!
70.plot: Jesse and Juliette take a trip to the video game store and then Jesse gets abandoned.

71.title: WHAT SHOULD I DO?
71.plot: Jesse asks for his viewers' help on whether he should go to his Uncle Larry's or back to his friend Zack's house.

72.title: SAYING GOODBYE
72.plot: Jesse says goodbye to Juliette and decides to stay with his Uncle Larry.

73.title: MEET UNCLE LARRY!
73.plot: Jesse leaves Juliette's school to return to New Jersey and live with his Uncle Larry.

74.title: SIGNS of PSYCHO UNCLE?
74.plot: Jesse films a "Day in the Life" at Uncle Larry's, but runs into some awkward situations when Uncle Larry disagrees with his way of life.

75.title: AN UNEXPECTED SURPRISE!
75.plot: Jesse goes to work with Uncle Larry and his Mom, only to find out that they have more than just "work" in mind for him.

76.title: VOICEMAIL from PSYCHO DAD!
76.plot: Jesse and Uncle Larry receive a message from Psycho Dad on the answering machine, leading them to make some dire decisions.

77.title: GETTING in TENTS!
77.plot: Jesse and Uncle Larry setup the new and improved, "Eagle's Landing 2.0".

78.title: WELCOME to PHOENIX LANDING!
78.plot: Jesse weathers a bad storm while introducing everyone to his brand new home.

79.title: THE JUGGIES LOUNGE!
79.plot: Jesse sets up the second tent and scavenges for different items for "thrival".

80.title: PSYCHO DAD SURPRISE VISIT
80.plot: Uncle Larry gets pissed at Jesse for hiding his beers and then Jesse's Dad shows up to the house.

81.title: JESSE CONFRONTS TOM!
81.plot: Tom apologizes to Jesse for ratting him out to his psychotic Father.

82.title: THE MAN in the RV!
82.plot: Jesse makes amends with Uncle Larry and Tom, buying food for everyone.

83.title: Paintball Prank REVERSAL! (Broken Lens)
83.plot: Jesse and Uncle Larry are forewarned about Jeffrey's paintball prank and decide to create a water-based ambush.

84.title: PSYCHO DAD FIGHTS UNCLE LARRY!
84.plot: While Uncle Larry and Jesse are cleaning up things from the paintball prank, Jesse's Psycho Dad appears.

85.title: MOVING INTO the RV!
85.plot: Jesse and Uncle Larry find Jeffrey's trophy smashing video and then Jesse moves into the RV.

86.title: I NEED YOUR HELP!
86.plot: Jesse asks for help from the Juggies.

87.title: WAKING UP to a MILLION!
87.plot: Jesse celebrates 1,000,000 Juggies and gets some reactions from Tom and Uncle Larry.

88.title: BALLIN' LIKE LARRY!
88.plot: Jesse and Uncle Larry go outside and shoot some hoops.

89.title: THE STORY of GARFUNKLE!
89.plot: Jesse and Uncle Larry pack up "Phoenix Landing" and the "Juggies Lounge". Garfunkle's origins are also revealed.

90.title: THE GAMING RV!
90.plot: Jesse gathers up whatever gaming materials he can and pimps out the RV. However, he's not the only one there.

91.title: The Juggies Powwow -- Suicide
91.plot: Jesse finally discusses the very serious issue of suicide and tries to tackle it gracefully.

92.title: UNCLE LARRY's RV FREAKOUT!
92.plot: Jesse shows Uncle Larry the graffiti on the side of the RV and also the video of the Juggies' letter to his Father.

93.title: I'M HOME.
93.plot: Jesse reveals to everyone that he's now back home...and okay.

94.title: Psycho Dad Reacts to One Million Juggies
94.plot: Jeffrey steals Uncle Larry's RV with Jesse still trapped inside. Their Dad appears making matters even worse.

1.title: The Wedding Confrontation!
1.plot: Jesse and his family attend a wedding together, but soon learn that there's still too many problems that need to be addressed.

2.title: BASKETBALL at UNCLE LARRY'S!
2.plot: Jesse takes a bike ride to Uncle Larry's for the coveted Sunday Basketball Experience.

3.title: JESSE GETS SWATTED!
3.plot: During his first Twitch live-stream back, Jesse, his family and his girlfriend get raided by the police because of a false call.

4.title: RETURN of the GENERATOR!
4.plot: Jesse, Juliette, and Buzz go on a crazy delivery trip to give Mr. H back his generator.

5.title: HOW MUCH MONEY DOES YOUTUBE PAY? - QnA #2
5.plot: Jesse answers more ridiculous questions in this second edition of the "QnA" series, talking about his Youtube earnings and what life was like living in a tent.

6.title: MOWING LAWNS with PSYCHO DAD!
6.plot: Jesse wakes up super late and prepares for his first day on the job...mowing lawns with his Father.

7.title: BETH the MAIL SORTER!
7.plot: After returning from mowing lawns, Jesse introduces everyone to Beth, the official fan mail sorter.

8.title: MOTHER's DAY BRUNCH!
8.plot: Jesse takes his Mother out for an awesome brunch at New Dodge's Market for Mother's Day.

9.title: LIFE BACK HOME *PSYCHO UPDATE*
9.plot: One week since being allowed back into the house, Jesse takes everyone through a "Day in his Life", showing the video-making process and also visits Uncle Larry and Tom.

10.title: The Juggies Powwow -- Procrastination
10.plot: In this Juggies Powwow, Jesse finally gets around to cleaning the pool while discussing the ever-so-pressing issue of procrastination.

11.title: JOURNEY to the NORTH!
11.plot: Jesse explains his previous video in more detail and then takes a road trip to North Jersey to see his girlfriend, Juliette.

12.title: JULIETTE's NEW CAR!
12.plot: Jesse and Juliette venture off to get a brand new car. Also, we meet Juliette's family.

13.title: Psycho Relationship Problems
13.plot: Jesse and Juliette get into a huge fight after Jesse's Dad yells at him for not returning home to mow lawns.

14.title: REALITY at a PRICE
14.plot: Jesse gets into a short fight with his Dad and talks about how many mistakes he's made.

15.title: A FAMILY JOB!
15.plot: Jesse learns he has to mow nine lawns with both his Dad and Brother.

16.title: Psycho Kid Gets Arrested
16.plot: An angry gamer gets fed up with working for his Dad and throws a tantrum in a store, leading to an arrest.

17.title: ARRESTED! *PSYCHO UPDATE*
17.plot: Jesse apologizes for everything that happened and Uncle Larry talks about some exciting news.

18.title: GAME of JUGGS! (UNCLE LARRY's CHANNEL)
18.plot: Jesse makes a gamble with Uncle Larry and challenges him to a game of "Horse", but this time the game is: "JUGGS". Jesse also introduces Uncle Larry's new Youtube channel.

19.title: The Juggies Powwow -- Growing Up & Getting Older
19.plot: Jesse and Uncle Larry discuss aging and different things to consider while growing up.

20.title: CHILLIN' & GRILLIN'!
20.plot: We get a taste of the type of grilling videos we could see on Uncle Larry's new channel and TOM LEAVES THE HOUSE.

21.title: CHAINSAWS, CONCOCTIONS & CORONAS!
21.plot: Uncle Larry goes swimming, while Jesse cuts down a tree with a chainsaw and Tom hoes a good job with Mario Kart.

22.title: MINI-GOLF COMPETITION!
22.plot: Jesse and Uncle Larry square off in an intense 36-hole mini-golf competition. Loser buys ice cream.

23.title: BIGBRUDDA IS a FREAK!
23.plot: Jesse says "Goodbye" to Uncle Larry and returns home to find Jeffrey celebrating the arrival of his Youtube Play Button.

24.title: PAYING RENT to PSYCHO DAD!
24.plot: Jesse gets extremely frustrated after seeing this month's bill he owes to his Father for living in the house.

25.title: SCENE of the CRIME
25.plot: Jesse returns to the store he got arrested in to apologize for what he did.

26.title: SCARED STRAIGHT
26.plot: Jesse confronts his Father about Joan claiming she never called the cops when he was arrested.

27.title: THE RETURN of CORN!
27.plot: Jesse announces his friend, Corn's, return to Youtube videos and also reveals a brand new "PSYCHO DAD" T-Shirt.

28.title: PRE-THERAPY SUGGESTIONS
28.plot: Jesse catches everybody up to speed with new merchandise, the stream and therapy tonight.

29.title: Psycho Family Therapy
29.plot: Dr. Nelson, a therapist, tries to mend fences with the Ridgway family, but her results are unsuccessful due to constant pointing fingers and arguing.

30.title: My Psychiatric Evaluation
30.plot: Two days after his family therapy session, Jesse updates everyone on his life.

31.title: JESSE WALKS THROUGH ASPHALT!
31.plot: Jesse tells the tragic story of how he walked through hot tar as an 8-year old boy, confining him to a wheelchair.

32.title: DONATING MONEY to CHARITY
32.plot: For 6-months of Fan Mail, Jesse donates $500.00 to a charity organization that cares for children from abusive households.

33.title: PSYCHO DAD T-SHIRTS & LIVESTREAM!
33.plot: Jesse gives a lackluster sales pitch for the new "Psycho Dad" shirts and announces tomorrow night's livestream.

34.title: VISITING UNCLE LARRY!
34.plot: Jesse drops off clothes for Tom at Uncle Larry's then clears out a room in the basement with Corn.

35.title: WHY DON'T YOU DRINK? - QnA #3
35.plot: In this 3rd "Question and Answer" video, Jesse answers questions about his Youtube Career and what it would be like to live on a deserted island.

36.title: Psycho Dad Buries Video Games
36.plot: An insane Father buries his son's video game collection after finding out he's being made fun of over the Internet.

37.title: DIGGING for GAMES! *Psycho Update*
37.plot: After Jesse's Dad buries all his video games, him and Corn decide to dig them all up.

38.title: THE LATE-NIGHT DIG!
38.plot: Jesse and Corn continue their digging well into the night.

39.title: THROW-OUT-YOUR-BACK THURSDAY!
39.plot: Jesse and Corn resume their digging for the lost Xbox 360 games that Jesse's Dad buried.

40.title: SPECIAL ANNOUNCEMENT!
40.plot: Jesse reveals some exciting news for next week.

41.title: JESSE vs the SPIDER!
41.plot: Jesse encounters an obnoxiously large spider in his room and tries to fight it.

42.title: THE TAYLOR SWIFT CONCERT!
42.plot: Jesse and Juliette prepare for T-Swift and give their thoughts on the concert.

43.title: JESSE GOES to LA!
43.plot: Jesse travels all the way from Southern New Jersey to Los Angeles for E3.

44.title: JESSE FAN-GIRLS at E3 2015!
44.plot: Jesse fan-girls and explores the trade floor of E3 at the Los Angeles Convention Center.

45.title: EXPLORING LOS SANTOS!
45.plot: Instead of spending all day at E3, Jesse decides to spread his wings and leave the nest, exploring the city of Los Santos...I mean, Los Angeles.

46.title: LAST DAY of E3 -- NINTENDO BOOTH
46.plot: Jesse heads to E3 for the final day of the convention to get some footage of Nintendo's upcoming titles.

94.plot: Jeffery decides to do a little prank on Jesse that goes a bit to far as he stomps on Jesses glasses and then a huge fight begins...

imdb.title: The Psycho Series
plot: The coming-of-age story of young Jesse Ridgway, with a new-age artistic passion, who has to stand up to his mischievous brother and old-world father, all the while slowly losing his mind.
